			<p>whatever@gmail.com</p>
			<h5>ADDRESS</h5>
			<p>18 Bridge Street<br/>Brooklyn,NY</p>
			<h5>PAYMENT</h5>
			<p>Real Soon<p>
		</div>


		<div class="col-md-7 my-profile-my-bio">
			<h1>My Bio<img src="<%= image_url 'edit_pencil.png' %>"/>
			</h1>
			<p>
				Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, quaeque accusam omnesque sea ea, dicunt persequeris quo et. Mel forensibus mnesarchum et. Sit scaevola ponderum ex. Ad error convenire posidonium mea. Cum vide primis in. Nibh equidem insolens ei pri, duo falli laoreet forensibus an. Veri oportere scripserit vis et, no usu maluisset contentiones
